Subject: [PATCH AUTOSEL 5.6 22/73] ASoC: Intel: atom: Take the drv->lock mutex before calling sst_send_slot_map()
Date:   Sat, 18 Apr 2020 09:47:24 -0400
Message-Id: <20200418134815.6519-22-sashal@kernel.org>
